{"tid":1532642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日有去東涌中學聲援嘅入晒黎！救人呀","createTime":"2019-09-02T14:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:12:16.000Z","uid":314141,"like":106,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdd2460ead0874c7a01f0a2d18e8d6ea5ed82e8","tid":1532642,"uid":314141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"話說就係今朝早有班廢老藍絲係保良局中學同標中之間圍屌聲援學生既舊生，有個白衫姐姐幫細路，跟住啲廢老攞個手機諗住打佢 白衫姐姐推開佢嘅手機然後而家俾人告刑事毁壞！😭😭😭俾人屈到上心口！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOE8UHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOE8UHy.jpg&h=a60bc788&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUha72z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUha72z.jpg&h=222bf925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地東涌人有完整片段做證，但狗要人證！！但舊生們大多都睇唔到（事件發生係距離學校大約百米既健康院果邊），因為有人拍片！所以證明左其實係有人睇到，但一直搵唔到拍片者！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加冇人知白衫姐姐點比d狗對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以唔該所有係今日11點到一點見到佢哋衝突可以做證嘅街坊請聯絡🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手做人證！"},{"pid":"269b9bffabe89c22e2476f7138c354e3656e5977","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:48:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b61098e552a9c5b7c40313c8df76c6094484d295","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f49fd2111a57d3a1de9e91688b5fc298090cff19","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:48:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7a81d6a9f1978bd62415275506403331fef8f3aa","tid":1532642,"uid":51007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:48:38.000Z","msg":"Push!<br />\n<br />\n東涌街坊幫幫手！<br />\n<br />\n如果你英文好的話 請以後發言中英對照 please recap ur comment in English<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aginiwU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aginiwU</a>"},{"pid":"dbb6179ea5852eaa65d9c5135922967ef28a4252","tid":1532642,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:48:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dt4dkj5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDt4dkj5.png&h=d03e935b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月8日<br />\n星期日<br />\n到美國領事館(遊行路線待定) <br />\n<br />\n唱住美國國歌 (下面有MV歌詞) <br />\n全力支持通過<br />\n《香港人權及民主法案》！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n[全登集氣]推到民陣搞，9月8號星期日大遊行，援請通過香港人權法！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531140\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531140</a><br />\n<br />\n美國人權及民主法案大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARgCLoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARgCLoO.jpg&h=045fa316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住練定美國國歌到時唱！！！！<br />\n </span></span><br />\n~~Oh, say can you see, <br />\nBy the dawn's early light, <br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed, <br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?~<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Click個play制聽下歌先啦！！！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soundcloud.com%2Fiahc%2Fusa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1atOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=7feaaf18\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.soundcloud.com/iahc/usa-national-anthem-star-spangled-banner</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vNfTjAM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvNfTjAM.gif&h=db1663f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">聽手足唱既版本真係會聽到流馬尿</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1atOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=b5679fd1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民發夢合唱</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: gold;\">We should learn how to sing</span><br />\n <em><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;The Star-</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">Spangled Banner&quot;</span></em><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZykHbrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZykHbrV.jpg&h=30a62641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">除咗九月八日，如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月一日</span>我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？<br />\n<br />\n而最重要，我地之前揮動美國國旗、唱美國國歌，美國傳媒一直都理解成我地係以追求人權民主自由既普世價值而表態！！！亦係動之以情地令佢地推動 香港人權及民主法案 既方法！！！<br />\n</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n九月八日發夢同我一齊唱！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=aS0Zid%2FrEVnhaHfkh5i1atOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=adfcf3ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSVsMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nSVsMz.png&h=279e88f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Make Hong Kong great again!</span><br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"c65a4b39e1d24e9df8c9a24428095cd20e1673df","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"19bd25103d89a0ddd6499857fa6920185a53cf1c","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:49:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c928e841b45acdcb7f7fdf97d8af1f81dddd3bd7","tid":1532642,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ac597ab9d52903e09b9bf84e0d71d302f4b0ca2","tid":1532642,"uid":165450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:49:29.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d64c4fd7aad379e3eeaf7977a3cc624f39eec5a","tid":1532642,"uid":295662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"推到有人證"},{"pid":"91afdbf201be6515894c0111b4c2da3c4243462d","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"175c424e59df4f61828afee358913ab61837b795","tid":1532642,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8aee6ce97ce611a02c94af89d633b8a10abcdecd","tid":1532642,"uid":9824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:53:26.000Z","msg":"