tedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81b034dc4418902ca51a17dda1366bbe52d98687","tid":1532642,"uid":287410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e48cfdb1946e338d151495cfbbdb3ef6b35638c3","tid":1532642,"uid":94223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:44:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7f43b9fb2060632c9685d7b3e75a1f523b57b26","tid":1532642,"uid":314141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9bdd2460ead0874c7a01f0a2d18e8d6ea5ed82e8","tid":1532642,"uid":314141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"話說就係今朝早有班廢老藍絲係保良局中學同標中之間圍屌聲援學生既舊生，有個白衫姐姐幫細路，跟住啲廢老攞個手機諗住打佢 白衫姐姐推開佢嘅手機然後而家俾人告刑事毁壞！😭😭😭俾人屈到上心口！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oOE8UHy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoOE8UHy.jpg&h=a60bc788&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LUha72z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLUha72z.jpg&h=222bf925&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地東涌人有完整片段做證，但狗要人證！！但舊生們大多都睇唔到（事件發生係距離學校大約百米既健康院果邊），因為有人拍片！所以證明左其實係有人睇到，但一直搵唔到拍片者！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加冇人知白衫姐姐點比d狗對待<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以唔該所有係今日11點到一點見到佢哋衝突可以做證嘅街坊請聯絡🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻🙌🏻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手做人證！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:46:36.000Z","msg":"補充少少！！<br />\n點解手足依加處於不利，係因為廢老打人果下好快（用腳踢），之後先有人過去開始拍片，令證據證明唔到手足係自衛，而見證到打人果下得周圍d藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2922aacd32613fd192f19dbd46d51cd71ea9b919","tid":1532642,"uid":101905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:47:20.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69a54b6e73bfa253828fa2305d6173c855736ab1","tid":1532642,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"e93185f3ffaaaf4bbbd61282fc8ab758fdb4c28f","tid":1532642,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"唔好報警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d733a16efff00ccf030aa871dc75b7b66b42ccf3","tid":1532642,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:55:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"006933fa5153fd4c1dc4a8b94071d7c88ef61a25","tid":1532642,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:55:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8414e6a82118854c06735b03fb6e012f14a4a1d9","tid":1532642,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:56:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"686311de7a2742d77c9eeb00ab3e9f28c01b7c3f","tid":1532642,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:57:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1011490993bbc97049f4b3a3201f936ca8120579","tid":1532642,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:00:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f794d9c4d16b42a0f187912b7eae2f67478870a8","tid":1532642,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:02:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fbb60ee37d989321f652e1e9667fbeedc7d299b","tid":1532642,"uid":111004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T17:05:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"304fcced23a6150d85e7d92e1dc111dd0efa80b5","tid":1532642,"uid":49066,"like":0,"dis